  "title": "Veterinarian",
  "description": "<p><strong>VetMedic Animal Clinic &amp; Surgery – We’re Hiring!</strong></p>\n<p>Are you a compassionate and dedicated Veterinarian looking to grow with a supportive team?<br>\nJoin us at <strong>VetMedic</strong>, a young and dynamic full-service veterinary clinic located in Sembawang. Our mission is simple: to deliver empathetic, passionate, and high-quality care to every patient who walks through our doors.</p>\n<h3>What We Offer</h3>\n<p>Our clinic is fully equipped to support both general practice and advanced veterinary care. You’ll have access to:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>IDEXX blood machines</li>\n  <li>Digital radiography &amp; dental radiography</li>\n  <li>Ultrasonography &amp; endoscopy</li>\n  <li>A comprehensive surgical suite, including Covidien Ligasure</li>\n  <li>A skilled and dedicated team of veterinary nurses to support your procedures</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Who We’re Looking For</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Experienced Veterinarians</strong> are strongly encouraged to apply</li>\n  <li><strong>Fresh graduates</strong> with the right attitude and passion are also welcome—we believe in nurturing new talent</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Growth Opportunities</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Hands-on learning in ultrasonography</li>\n  <li>Opportunities to get started with orthopaedic surgeries</li>\n  <li>Subsidies for continuing education courses, both local and overseas</li>\n</ul>\n<p>At VetMedic, you’ll not only find a workplace but also a team that values growth, collaboration, and genuine care—for pets and for each other.</p>",
